Package: bunddev
Title: Discover and Call 'Bund.dev' APIs
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Bücker", ,
        "michael.buecker@fh-muenster.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0045-8460"))
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Description: Provides a registry of APIs listed on <https://bund.dev>
        and a core 'OpenAPI' client layer to explore specs and perform
        requests. Adapter helpers return tidy tibbles for supported
        APIs, with optional response caching and rate limiting
        guidance.
